window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>She's a tiny thing, so young and na√Øve.<br> Beautiful and brave but loyal to a fault.<br> She needs the firm hand of a strong man. </p> <p>Just...not my own. <br> She was meant to marry one of my brothers.<br> I never wanted a ring on my own finger.</p> <p>But now I want to put my hands on her.<br> Tear her innocence away from her. <br> Be the first and the only man to touch her.</p> <p>I can't get her out of my mind.<br> I've gone from wanting to punish her...<br> To wanting to make her mine.</p> <p><i>Forever.</i></p> <p><b><i>Vow to the King</i></b><b> is a fully stand-alone novel with darker themes, hot scenes, and a hard-won happily ever after. This highly addictive mafia world is like no other you've read. Welcome to Shanna Handel's Bachman Family.</b></p>"; 
